data.name: RichTextBox.Text
data.value:
To use this app start with a right click on a folder to call the context menu and select WinThumbsPreloader > Preload thumbnails in the menu.
Also you can launch the app from command line: Usage: WinThumbsPreloader.exe [-r] <path> Options: -r Recursively preload thumbnails in nested folders. -s Silent mode - don't show a progress dialog.
Apropos Dmitry Bruhov https://github.com/bruhov/WinThumbsPreloader
